column5: A friend of mine is looking for a Yamaha kicker, around 5 hp or so. Does anyone have a dealer in GTA to recommend?
Central Outboard Marine in markham just north of lebarons on woodbine north of hwy 7
there is a used one in the classified section , only 4 hp though.
J & P Marine.... just off the highway in Belleville. Just got a 50 hp yamaha and was looking at a kicker and they had some for sale at low prices. google the name and its the first link...
Thanks SoDa. Mikeh, the one in the classified has a short shaft. What my friend needs is a long shaft. Wait, that came out a bit funny. LOL.
